short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Call phone numbers on a webpage using voiceetc c2c.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension is developed for voice-etc (https://voiceetc.co.in) a cloud based telecom service provider and we have many cloud based telecom services

Click to call is one of our service , this is provided to only registered users or service subscribed users of voice-etc  and this extension will help the users to call their customer from user's, CRM, ERP or webpages where they want to call their own clients or customers

This application will send selected phone numbers on webpage to our API along with the client API key and User ID. The API will originate call from our server to user's number (This extension logged in user's phone number given in our portal) Once answered the call we will dial the selected number from webpage 

This extension can be use only by the users who have subscribed and active with our click to call services
